{
  "stem": "151.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course until my brother was in labor camp, they had contact but after that they didn't.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She also became very ill during hiding time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, as a matter of fact, if I recall the first time when I went back home, she came with me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember the Russian commander was in our home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I walked in and I told him that I'm the [NON-ENGLISH] and that I owned the home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, oh, that's all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Pick a room.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would let me stay in a room if I want to stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I realized that that's not the way l want to live and I'm not going to be there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And also our housekeeper, or old housekeeper lived upstairs in a little apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she pretended that she was delighted that we came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, I'm sure she was worried that I'm going to ask back for the things that she probably took from our home, which I had no intentions doing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't want anything from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she asked me what should she make for us to eat and I said to her take two dozen eggs and make dumplings out of them and then take two more dozen eggs and beat it like scrambled eggs over it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my sister-in-law-- now she's my sister-in-law, my brother's girlfriend-- the two of us sat down and ate the dumplings with the scrambled eggs, which was a big pot.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we went back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took a little package where I found, as I said before, my father's gold watch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother's bar mitzvah watch and my gold bracelet that my father bought me for my 18th birthday.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
